<h2>Reset Your Password</h2>

<p>Hi<% if (userName) { %> <strong><%= userName %></strong><% } %>,</p>

<p>We received a request to reset the password for your account associated with <strong><%= email %></strong>.</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
</p>

<p class="muted">This link will expire in <%= expiryHours || 1 %> hour<%= (expiryHours || 1) > 1 ? 's' : '' %> for security.</p>

<hr class="divider">

<p class="muted">
  If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:
</p>

<div class="code-box">
  <%= resetUrl %>
</div>

<div class="alert-box alert-warning">
  <strong>Didn't request this?</strong><br>
  If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.
  <br><br>
  If you're concerned about your account security, we recommend changing your password immediately from your account settings.
</div>

<p class="muted">
  For security, this request was received from IP address <%= ipAddress || 'unknown' %><% if (userAgent) { %> using <%= userAgent %><% } %>.
</p>
